  "title": "🔥Customer & People Engagement Sales Associate",
  "description": "<p>Looking for a dynamic role that offers growth, exposure, and strong team collaboration? This opportunity provides hands-on experience, clear progression, and a fast-paced, supportive environment.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Support interactive brand initiatives and public-facing campaigns</p></li><li><p>Engage the public to create positive, in-person brand experiences</p></li><li><p>Collaborate closely with a motivated team to achieve shared objectives</p></li></ul><p><strong>What You’ll Gain:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Regional exposure with diverse project involvement</p></li><li><p>Structured training, coaching, and continuous development</p></li><li><p>Clear career progression based on performance</p></li><li><p>A positive and energetic team culture</p></li></ul><p>If you enjoy working with people, learning on the job, and growing within a results-driven team, this role offers a strong platform to build your career.</p><p>📩 <strong>Apply now to learn more.</strong></p>",
